OL,3,CMan charged with murder after body
OL,4,Cfound
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the death of
OL,7,Fa man in Margate have charged a
OL,8,Fsuspect with murder.
OL,10,FKent Police was called to a property
OL,11,Fin the High Street shortly after
OL,12,F11:30am on Thursday 11 June, following
OL,13,Fconcerns for a person's welfare.
OL,15,FOfficers attended and located the body
OL,16,Fof a man inside.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
