CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781470069
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after body
OL,4,Cfound
OL,6,FFormal identification has not yet
OL,7,Ftaken place, but the family of 31-year-
OL,8,Fold Nathan Jermy, who had previously
OL,9,Fbeen reported missing, have been
OL,10,Finformed.
OL,12,FBradley Cooper, 40, of Eaton Road,
OL,13,FMargate, was arrested later that day
OL,14,Fand has now been charged with murder.
OL,16,FHe has been remanded in custody, to
OL,17,Fappear before Margate Magistrates'
OL,18,FCourt on Monday 15 June.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
