PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781470069
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after body
OL,4,Cfound
OL,6,FThree other people have also been
OL,7,Farrested in connection with the
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FAshleigh Muir, 33, of High Street,
OL,11,FMargate, has been charged with
OL,12,Fassisting an offender and she has also
OL,13,Fbeen remanded in custody to appear at
OL,14,Fthe same court hearing.
OL,16,FA 30-year-old man has been released on
OL,17,Fbail pending further enquiries, while
OL,18,Fa 17-year-old girl remains in custody.
